 sources: (1) AI responses to FAQ tickets were more consistent and complete than the agents had been — no variation based on who was working, no copy-paste errors. (2) Agents now only handled genuinely complex tickets, and their quality on those improved because they weren't burned out on repetitive questions."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"mb-14","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-3 mb-5","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[#c9a84c]","children":"04"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[#5a5550]","children":"The System Prompt"}]]}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-[24px] font-light text-[#f0ede8] mb-5 leading-snug","children":"The exact customer service prompt — copy-paste ready"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-[15px] text-[#9a9590] leading-relaxed mb-6","children":"This prompt is used for Tier 1 auto-resolutions. The user message is a JSON object containing the ticket text, customer order history, and relevant product data from Shopify. Customize the bracketed fields for your brand."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"relative","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-8 bg-[#0d0d0d] border border-[#1e1e1e] border-b-0 flex items-center px-4 gap-2","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#1e1e1e]"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#1e1e1e]"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#1e1e1e]"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"ml-auto font-mono text-[10px] text-[#5a5550]","children":"SYSTEM PROMPT — Customer Service (Tier 1)"}]]}],["$","pre",null,{"className":"mt-8 bg-[#0a0a0a] border border-[#1e1e1e] p-5 text-[12px] text-[#9a9590] leading-relaxed overflow-x-auto whitespace-pre-wrap font-mono","children":"$3"}]]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"mb-14","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-